Time spent in this assignment: 10 hours

My assessment:
Before taking this course, I had no experience in SQL databases and their use with python. This assignment thus resulted incredibly helpful not only to understand the relations between different tables in a database, but also to learn best practices in querying information from them. It was also helpful to learn modules such as textwrap and argparse, which I will use in future programs. I think this assignment serves its purpose fittingly and I wouldn't change anything for future years.